snippet.title: Hobs | Trailer
snippet.description:
Hobs is a turn based card game which you can try different strategies to beat your opponent.

Find best deck for your strategy, buy new heros, try different strategies and try to place to the top.

Now you can download and play from Steam and Google Play Store for free!

Steam: http://bit.ly/2ZdFjaz
Play Store: http://bit.ly/30exYVm
Web Sitesi: http://hobsgame.com/

Donate: https://www.oyunfor.com/twitch-donate...

Discord: https://discord.gg/AUw97wu
Youtube: http://bit.ly/2KHaQtf
